textBox.richText: Gunter came out again this weekend, and we got *another* shot of snow (yay!) Alli met up with Caitlin, Miles, and Carolyn on Saturday, and convinced them to stay Saturday night. Gunter convinced Michelle to come out Sunday...so we had a sizeable crew on the hill. Got some film of Max doing Pony, and showed ‘em around the sleepy trees and Eagle. Max’s gloves were cold, so swapped out with Mom over at Pioneer, where after a lunch break, convinced him to get going again. Met up with Matthias and Ray over there...did a couple laps before Mom and Max did a lunch break. Gunter, Michelle, and I then finished out the day...
